sequenceDiagram
    autonumber
    participant Owner as Site Owner
    participant Studio as Sanity Studio
    participant YouTube as YouTube API
    participant Content as Sanity Content Lake
    participant CLI as Developer CLI
    participant CF as Cloudflare Pages
    participant Site as Live Website

    Note over Owner,Site: Add New Video Workflow

    Owner->>Studio: Navigate to Videos
    Owner->>Studio: Click + (new video)
    Owner->>Studio: Paste YouTube URL
    Owner->>Studio: Click dropdown arrow next to Publish
    Owner->>Studio: Select "Fetch from YouTube"

    Studio->>YouTube: GET /videos?id={videoId}
    YouTube-->>Studio: Video metadata (title, description, duration, thumbnail)

    Studio->>Studio: Auto-populate fields
    Owner->>Studio: Select Category
    Owner->>Studio: Click Publish

    Studio->>Content: Save video document

    Note over Owner,Site: Deploy to Live Site

    Owner->>CLI: Request deploy
    CLI->>CLI: npm run build
    CLI->>CLI: Create deploy_package
    Owner->>CF: Upload via Cloudflare Dashboard
    CF->>Content: Fetch all content (build time)
    CF->>CF: Generate static pages
    CF-->>Site: Deploy to CDN

    Note over Owner,Site: Video now visible on live site
